snippet.textDisplay: The reason it smells bad is because most cheap instant coffee (expired or not) is very salty. So if it smells like Soy Sauce, you know that the coffee you're making won't taste as good as a more expensive instant coffee. I used fresh instant coffee (cheap) and it didn't taste all that great, but while mixing it, the stuff smelled like Soy Sauce and I hated it.
